msg: Adding $rootFontFamily to the dispatcher pdf (actually FO) generation, by injecting the relevant value into one contract, and then extracting that value in the final processing step, and add it at the correct place.
It is perhaps not the most beautiful solution, but it works, and it keeps the dispatcher and skins-based FO processing similar.
